{"tid":437850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法媒頭版「中國，強國崛起」專題","createTime":"2017-10-16T11:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T11:14:54.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a59368a0211aa6693677f967e3df90fb0a8232","tid":437850,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">　內地官媒紛報道後發現中伏</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B3%95%E5%AA%92%E9%A0%AD%E7%89%88-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BC%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7-%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E7%B4%9B%E8%BD%89%E8%BC%89%E5%BE%8C%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2589%2588-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B4%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%25B4%259B%25E8%25BD%2589%25E8%25BC%2589%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BC%258F%2F&d=B4b75f0mo7NkddIn%2FBdIGW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c7338586\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2589%2588-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B4%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592%25E7%25B4%259B%25E8%25BD%2589%25E8%25BC%2589%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BC%258F%2F&h=30c9063b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B3%95%E5%AA%92%E9%A0%AD%E7%89%88-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BC%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7-%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92%E7%B4%9B%E8%BD%89%E8%BC%89%E5%BE%8C%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國媒體《世界報》週日刊出的號外專刊，頭版以簡體中文寫著「中國，強國崛起」，獲中國官媒《環球時報》、中央電視紛紛報導。不過，報導指法國《世界報》文章內容其實有不少篇幅是諷刺中國內政，環時及央視隨後急忙將有關報導下架。<br />\n<br />\n在google搜尋器的結果可見，環時、央視昨日曾發布以「法媒頭版中文大標題介绍&ldquo;强國崛起&rdquo;：我們已經進入了中國世紀」、「法國《世界報》頭版：中國，强國崛起」為題的新聞報導，不過有關網頁今日已經被移除。<br />\n<br />\n自由時報報導指，不少中國網民發現官媒弄錯法國媒體意思後，紛紛於微博上留言質疑，但批評的留言一個一個「被消失」。<br />\n<br />\n據法國國際廣播電台（RFI）報道，鑑於中共十九屆黨代表大會將於後日（18日）召開，《世界報》於週日出版關於中國的號外專刊，其中用了8頁篇幅關注中國社會變遷。專刊亦談及有關中國加大對企業集團控制，打壓律師及記者，及嚴控網絡活動等議題。<br />\n<br />\nRFI報導引述該報國際部副主任Fran&ccedil;ois Bougon在編者論寫到，相信將會連任的習近平向世界提出與美國不同的「中國夢」選擇，並於世界舞台上與美國抗衡。Bougon認為，「中國夢」在外交及領土問題上充滿雄心和策略，一改從1970年開始的韜光養晦的策略，以中國崛起為目標，令亞洲鄰國擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lemonde-07_hZfOD_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flemonde-07_hZfOD_1200x0.png&h=940fbff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/1cctv_vanjl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F1cctv_vanjl_1200x0.png&h=a21d7e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cctv404_wHRX5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcctv404_wHRX5_1200x0.png&h=1b0a84bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/huanqiu1_cxs5w_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhuanqiu1_cxs5w_1200x0.png&h=cec0b534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/huanqiu_k0tA9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhuanqiu_k0tA9_1200x0.png&h=b657fd06&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}